    "description": "<strong>概述</strong><br><br><strong>《Snowmen》</strong>是一款<strong>童话</strong>般的短篇恐怖游戏，你必须收集不寻常的材料并躲避来自异界的<strong>危险</strong>，<strong>逃离</strong>地狱般的雪域环境！<br><br><strong>游戏</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325770/extras/ab7378a2867a0e99612a0bc1fd6de20e.poster.avif?t=1742038507\" width=598 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325770/extras/ab7378a2867a0e99612a0bc1fd6de20e.webm?t=1742038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325770/extras/ab7378a2867a0e99612a0bc1fd6de20e.mp4?t=1742038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>不断<strong>移动</strong>，因为时间紧迫，<strong>危险</strong>就在近旁！<br></li><li><strong>收集、收集、收集，以及</strong>……<strong>快跑！！！</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325770/extras/c3e488f6dc3ff9d9cdafda8faed10bbb.poster.avif?t=1742038507\" width=598 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325770/extras/c3e488f6dc3ff9d9cdafda8faed10bbb.webm?t=1742038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325770/extras/c3e488f6dc3ff9d9cdafda8faed10bbb.mp4?t=1742038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>探索</strong>你所受困的看似无限的世界！<br></li><li>借助<strong>地标</strong>和<strong>音频</strong>提示进行<strong>搜索</strong>和导航！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325770/extras/b11179c8a9d06e50c01d1d7656c3020a.poster.avif?t=1742038507\" width=598 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325770/extras/b11179c8a9d06e50c01d1d7656c3020a.webm?t=1742038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325770/extras/b11179c8a9d06e50c01d1d7656c3020a.mp4?t=1742038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>与环境及其奇怪但熟悉的居民进行<strong>互动</strong> ，以获取有用的信息！<br></li><li><strong>选择</strong>很重要，所以要小心你的行动！</li></ul><br><strong>剧情</strong><br><br>这是一个童话故事般的短篇恐怖游戏。你因为过于<strong>淘气</strong>被赶出了<strong>家门</strong>！<br><br>你受到了不负责任的不公平对待，于是准备开始新的生活！<br>但人生不如意事十之八九，事情的发展并不像你打算的那样……<br><br>但这次情况不同……总不会<strong>有魔法</strong>吧，对不对？<br>尤其是在这个充满爱的神圣幸福的时刻、合家团聚的佳节！！<br><br>……哦，等等。<br><br>你已经不再拥有那个幸福时刻，也找不到前方的<strong>路</strong>，因为你已经迷失了。<br>不过，你并不是孤身一人，不管这是好事还是坏事。<br><br>……多半是坏事。<br><br>那些关于送来礼物的好心人的古老故事似乎也都是谎言，不能相信。<br>那么在这个<strong>寒冷的恶梦疆域</strong>里，你能相信谁呢？<br><br>你唯一能做的就是<strong>继续前进</strong>并找到回家的路。<br>希望总不会完全丧失的，对吧？！",
